      <h3><i class="fa fa-fw fa-location-arrow"></i> Shareholder Api Routes</h3>
  </div>

  <ul>
      <li><code>{shareholder}</code> must be the integer ID of a Shareholder.</li>
      <li><code>{format}</code> must be <code>XML</code> or <code>JSON</code> (if not provided the default is <code>JSON</code>).</li>
  </ul>

  <hr/>

  <div class="panel panel-default">
